---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="About"
  description="Offensive Security Engineer building systems at the intersection of security, automation, and AI."
>
  <section class="about">
    <div class="header">
      <h1>Himanshu Gupta</h1>
      <span class="role">Offensive Security Engineer</span>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <p>I work on breaking systems and understanding how they fail.</p>
      <p>
        My focus is offensive security across web, APIs, mobile, infrastructure, and cloud.
        I approach testing as system analysis.
      </p>
      <p>
        I build tools to remove manual work, scale attack workflows, and uncover
        vulnerabilities faster.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <h2>Current Direction</h2>
      <p>
        Combining offensive security with AI to create systems that can:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>automate reconnaissance</li>
        <li>triage vulnerabilities</li>
        <li>generate and test attack paths</li>
      </ul>
      <p class="goal">
        Move from human-driven testing to <strong>system-driven offense</strong>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <h2>Work</h2>
      <ul class="work-list">
        <li>
          <span class="work-title">Penetration Testing</span>
          <span class="work-desc">Web applications, APIs, mobile (Android/iOS), network infrastructure, cloud environments, and secure code reviews. Full-scope and targeted engagements.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="work-title">Tool Development</span>
          <span class="work-desc">Custom recon pipelines, Burp extensions, and offensive tooling built for real-world use.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="work-title">AI-Assisted Offense</span>
          <span class="work-desc">LLM-augmented recon, automated triage, and payload generation for modern attack surfaces.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="work-title">Automation</span>
          <span class="work-desc">End-to-end attack workflows, CI/CD security integration, and scalable bug bounty systems.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="work-title">Bug Bounty</span>
          <span class="work-desc">Active on HackerOne and Bugcrowd.</span>
        </li>
        <li>
          <span class="work-title">Content</span>
          <span class="work-desc">Technical deep-dives, labs, and security education.</span>
        </li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <h2>Certification</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>eWPTX — Web Application Penetration Tester eXtreme v2</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="block">
      <h2>Contact</h2>
      <div class="contact-list">
        <p class="contact-row">
          <span class="label">email</span>
          <a href="mailto:himanshugupta2077@gmail.com">himanshugupta2077@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
        <p class="contact-row">
          <span class="label">linkedin</span>
          <a href="https://linkedin.com/in/himanshugupta2077" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">linkedin.com/in/himanshugupta2077</a>
        </p>
        <p class="contact-row">
          <span class="label">github</span>
          <a href="https://github.com/himanshugupta2077" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">github.com/himanshugupta2077</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .about {
    max-width: 600px;
  }

  .header {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h1 {
    font-size: 1.375rem;
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .block {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  h2 {
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.1em;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  p {
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
  }

  .goal {
    margin-top: 0.75rem;
  }

  ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  li {
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: var(--text);
    padding: 0.3rem 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border);
  }

  li:last-child {
    border-bottom: none;
  }

  li::before {
    content: '→ ';
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .work-list li {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.2rem;
    padding: 0.5rem 0;
  }

  .work-list li::before {
    display: none;
  }

  .work-title {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--text);
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .work-title::before {
    content: '→ ';
    color: var(--green);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
  }

  .work-desc {
    font-size: 0.825rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    padding-left: 1.25rem;
  }

  .contact-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
  }

  .contact-row {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 1rem;
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .label {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    min-width: 5rem;
  }

  .contact-row a {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: var(--green);
  }
</style>
